
//
// ping reader
//
// simple hack which reads the input from the parallax ping every second
//
// author: @jefforulez
//

//
// parts
//

; arduino uno rev 2
: http://arduino.cc/en/Main/arduinoBoardUno

; makershield w/ mini breadboard
: http://www.makershed.com/MakerShield_p/msms01.htm

; parallax ping sensor
: http://www.parallax.com/tabid/768/ProductID/92/Default.aspx

; various jumpers

//
// wiring
//

// PING

1. PING 5V to Arduino 5V
2. PING GND to Arduino GND
3. PING Signal to Arduino D7
